# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok over ## percent of russian enterprises and companies made profits , while ## percent lost money in the first ## months this year , a report from the state committee for statistics said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (r / report-01
            :ARG0 (c / committee
                  :mod (s2 / state)
                  :mod (s3 / statistics)))
      :ARG1 (c2 / contrast-01
            :ARG1 (p / profit-01
                  :ARG0 (a / and
                        :op1 (e / enterprise
                              :mod (c3 / country
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Russia")))
                        :op2 (c4 / company
                              :mod c3)
                        :quant (o / over
                              :op1 (p2 / percentage-entity
                                    :value 1))))
            :ARG2 (l / lose-02
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (m / money)
                  :time (m2 / month
                        :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1)
                        :mod (y / year
                              :mod (t / this)))))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the suicide bomber whose explosive-laden car killed ## people in a downtown street appeared to be attempting a direct strike at the main police station , algiers newspapers said tuesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (n / newspaper
            :location (c / city
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Algiers")))
      :ARG1 (a / appear-02
            :ARG1 (a2 / attempt-01
                  :ARG0 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (b / bomb-01
                              :mod (s2 / suicide))
                        :poss-of (c2 / car
                              :ARG1-of (l / load-01
                                    :ARG2 (e / explosive))
                              :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
                                    :ARG1 (p2 / person)
                                    :location (s3 / street
                                          :mod (d / downtown)))))
                  :ARG1 (s4 / strike-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (s5 / station
                              :mod (p3 / police)
                              :mod (m / main))
                        :ARG1-of (d2 / direct-02))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :polarity -

                                    :mod (v / video)))
                        :location (a2 / and
                              :op1 (r / restaurant)
                              :op2 (e / establish-01)))
                  :time (e2 / ever))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday)))
      :op2 (s2 / support-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (b / ban-01
                  :ARG1 g2

                        :op1 (s3 / store

                        :op2 (s4 / store

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok sam cassell scored ## of his ## points in the fourth quarter , including four free throws in the final ##.# seconds , as the phoenix suns defeated utah ##-## thursday , snapping the jazz 's league-leading ##-game winning streak .

                  :op2 " cassell"))

            :poss p
            :ARG2-of (ii / include-91
                  :ARG1 (f / free-03
                        :quant 4
                        :time (f2 / final
                              :op1 (s2 / second)))))
      :ARG2 (q / quarter
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 4))
      :time (d / defeat-01
            :ARG0 (s3 / sun
                  :mod (p3 / phoenix))
            :ARG1 p
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "utah"))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :ARG0-of (s4 / snap-04
            :ARG1 (s5 / streak
                  :mod (w / win-01
                        :ARG0 (j / jazz))
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (l2 / league)))))

# ::alignments
(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (w / win-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Charles"
                        :op2 "Cheruiyot")
                  :mod (c / city
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Kenya")))
            :ARG1 (m2 / marathon
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 " graz"))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / sunday))
            :manner (c2 / clock-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (m3 / multiple
                        :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (m4 / minute)))))
      :snt2 (b / be-located-at-91
            :ARG1 (m5 / minute)
            :ARG2 (r / relative-position
                  :op1 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (c3 / compete-02
                              :ARG1 p)
                        :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (n4 / near-02
                                    :ARG1 p2)
                              :ARG3 (m6 / most)
                              :ARG5 p))
                  :direction (a / ahead)
                  :quant (n5 / nearly
                        :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 4
                              :unit (m7 / minute))))))
